<span id="freeTextContainer2479801091289757935">I enjoyed Midnight Never Ends. It reminded me of shows that i watched religiously, The Outer Limits and Twilight Zone series. No Body Dies On The First Floor and Along For The Ride were my favorite. I absolutely loved the book cover and the title fits the collection of stories. If you enjoy classic horror, consider reading Midnight Never Ends.</span>

          </span>
